Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.79,0:22:43.66,Wing ED Lyrics,ED Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Hashittekitano wakatterukedo\N{\c&H00FF00&}I know he's out of breath from running here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.93,0:22:47.09,Wing ED Lyrics,ED Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Sonna koto wa atari mae yo!\N{\c&H00FF00&}But that's the very least he could do for me!
