Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.48,0:23:02.40,Wing ED Lyrics,ED Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Ijiwaru wo schichau no wa sukidakara yo\N{\c&H00FF00&}I only tease him because I actually like him...
