Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.23,0:23:21.06,Wing ED Lyrics,ED Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fs85.5\c&H00FF00&}Just love...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.88,0:23:29.89,Wing Next Episode Text,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,760.5)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.75,0:23:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,With the Gundams' arrival,\Nthe true battle has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.59,0:23:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But is it what the\Ncolonies desire?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.63,0:23:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice Foreign Minister Darlian\Nleaves for the colonies again...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.29,0:23:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...taking Relena with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.73,0:23:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But OZ's Lady Une plans\Nthe Minister's assassination.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.47,0:23:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,With Minister Darlian's\Ndying breath...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.50,0:23:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...Relena learns the secrets\Nsurrounding her birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.04,0:23:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, on Gundam Wing, Episode 5,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.91,0:23:58.60,Wing Next Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\be7\blur6.75\pos(720,731.25)}Relena's Secret
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.94,0:23:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"Relena's Secret".
